            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer against blacksmiths and sorcerers, employing the names allegedly revealed to 
                    <persName ref="PRS8925Solomon"/>. The prayer employs similar <term key="Asmat">ʾasmāt</term>, shares the same 
                    connection to Solomon, and is likewise directed against blacksmiths, as is the case with
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7367PPLaNahabt"/>.</p>
